### 解题思路

此处撰写解题思路

### 代码

* java

```java
class Solution {
    public int maxProfit(int[] prices) {

        int[] profits = new int[2];

        profits[0] = -prices[0];
        profits[1] = 0;

        int max = 0;

        for(int i = 1;i<prices.length;i++) {

            profits[0] = Integer.max(profits[0], -prices[i]);

            profits[1] = Integer.max(profits[1], prices[i] + profits[0]); 

        } 

        return profits[1];


    }
}
```

